Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.70,0:01:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們應該知道是誰在等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天劍宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.64,0:01:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是以前把我的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.64,0:02:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分成兩半的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.74,0:02:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.95,0:02:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現在的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.92,0:02:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學會逆刃刀的真髓\N與絕招天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且最主要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.96,0:02:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是場絕不能輸的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.58,0:02:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五十四話\N飛天對縮地\N宗次郎天賦的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.76,0:02:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高興您平安無事來到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為是什麼樣的英雄豪傑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是跟劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打成平手的弱男子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.17,0:03:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你有禮的問侯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.87,0:03:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很不巧 我沒有時間\N與你慢慢愉快談天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.98,0:03:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問你是要立刻退開\N還是跟我交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.51,0:03:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間？你是說葵屋的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.62,0:03:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才收到電報 我們輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.19,0:03:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治大吃一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但 事實就是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而相對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次換成我沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必需一個人完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.31,0:03:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀十人份的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法在緋村一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身上浪費太多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟新月村一樣的拔刀術的對抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.17,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好什麼好 只是一個小小的缺口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟平手差不多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次你帶著一把好刀哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.92,0:04:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然外觀看不出特殊的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.65,0:05:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的愛刀 菊一文字則宗\N這下子有瑕疵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.19,0:05:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菊一文字是超越長曾虎徹的\N傳說中的名刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.93,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刀是一流的\N用刀的人更是超一流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.87,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的交手就出現缺口\N就顯示了實力的差異了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管上次交手的記錄怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.17,0:05:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心的拔刀術\N比他更快 幹得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你進步了 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你本來就已經很強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.95,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還能變得更強 真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.49,0:05:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我也很訝異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼像你這樣的人\N能變得那麼強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正你是絕敵不過志志雄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要認真起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會輸給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個腳力…原來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.69,0:06:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保卿坐在行進的馬車上\N被這個青年暗殺身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是死在他這能力上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 沒中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次殺死他就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.07,0:06:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 剛才那麼快\N跟劍心的神速不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.44,0:06:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 如果我的眼睛沒看錯\N剛才他比劍心快…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.61,0:06:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能 世上不可能有人\N可以移動得比劍心更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才他的行動是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.32,0:06:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先前不是一直吹牛說\N他很強 很厲害嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.89,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是因為志志雄大人\N認為他厲害才那麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個小弟弟出手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那樣說話沒根據  不慚愧嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格指責我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縮地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.67,0:07:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那是超越神速的超神速「縮地」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是純正的劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直不知道那個名詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是志志雄大人告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.22,0:07:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縮地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是宗次郎在天劍\N缺乏感情之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有的第三個能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以那強韌的腳力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一下子就從起跑達到最高速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.74,0:07:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬間侵入對方防備距離的\N傳說中的身法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.74,0:07:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彷彿使用法術縮短距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.05,0:07:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來像瞬間移動一樣\N因而被稱為縮地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.45,0:07:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 縮地是指\N快得人眼看不見的速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.29,0:07:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 那只能用來\N稱呼拔刀齊的神速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎的超神速、縮地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是快得肉眼看不見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.53,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊的厲害點在於
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.97,0:08:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讀出對手的感情與動向\N先發制人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.24,0:08:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是宗次郎沒有感情 他的動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.58,0:08:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊就無法洞察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.28,0:08:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎有拔刀齊看不見的\N超神速 縮地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊活下來的可能性是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.43,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是緋村 老實說\N剛才那個不是縮地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.34,0:08:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確說來\N還比縮地慢上三步呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.68,0:08:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你眼睛才能看到 避過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.18,0:08:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從在新月村打成平手的速度推算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.72,0:08:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本以為這樣就能打敗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.19,0:08:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 我好像太輕視你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.83,0:09:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次就以比縮地還慢二步\N的速度來進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別停下來 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會被瞄準的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.63,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是腳 身手也很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.47,0:09:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且因為無法讀取他的情緒\N而感覺更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比原本的還快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別被對手的速度迷惑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用正面交差法倒拿武士刀\N破解他的神速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.72,0:09:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學會絕招天翔龍閃時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時學得的這一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九頭龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.83,0:10:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 真正的現在才開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.51,0:10:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他避開了完全\N無法防禦跟迴避的九頭龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.58,0:11:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎這個人果然比我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.85,0:11:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、比飛天御劍流更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.99,0:11:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭一次看到\N比劍心還要快的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.26,0:11:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次有人砍傷劍心的背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙 這次真的不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.43,0:11:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.93,0:11:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 天劍宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比緋村拔刀齊更強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再一劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次攻擊一定可以讓他死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了 我還以為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定殺死他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然  奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.02,0:11:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最初還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.06,0:11:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才我是瞄準緋村\N施絕招後的空隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.79,0:11:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼還殺不了他 怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹掉他 劍心\N他現在全身是破綻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.87,0:11:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟 別想那個了\N快點把他幹掉呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有犯下任何錯誤呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.24,0:12:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世間是弱肉強食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.15,0:12:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者生 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒是想使盡全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.88,0:12:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把壓抑在緋村劍心體內\N的斬人拔刀齊拖出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不只是厲害而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 你在發什麼呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢？你說誰蠢 沒禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是比你還有社會經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.01,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 剛才不是說你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.41,0:12:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角他說你是怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.89,0:12:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼說那種話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角是誰呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角？小弟弟 你在想什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以問你一個問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那時候你使出龍翔閃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍翔閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.24,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故意讓志志雄知道你的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.71,0:13:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你連那個都不懂\N是不是頭殼壞了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候志志雄對尖角說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不能引劍心使出絕招\N就要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以劍心才使出絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了救尖角一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.59,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算對手是敵人\N也忍不住產生感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心就是這樣一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.73,0:14:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候你應該殺死尖角的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因為你沒殺死  讓他活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他才說出奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.51,0:14:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 我怎麼浪費時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定會殺死你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定要收拾他哦  小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.02,0:14:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以比縮地慢一步的速度…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.00,0:14:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟剛才比起來  劍速慢了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該殺死他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候你應該殺死尖角的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫你沒殺死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做那麼怪異的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太意外了  你還會使計逃走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,午安 尖角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來殺我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.95,0:15:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒讓你知道什麼重要秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.09,0:15:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不值得殺的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.29,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人是這麼講的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.69,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角 你為什麼活著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.13,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你輸給緋村了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒有殺死我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是沒有他的一念之仁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早被志志雄大人殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浮在血池地獄中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.91,0:16:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而現在卻能躺在這裏曬太陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊不只是厲害而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是另一種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.02,0:16:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟志志雄那種以恐懼\N來控制人是不一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.89,0:16:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼搞的 我實在無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不殺死他  緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不殺死他  緋村……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世間弱肉強食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者生 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有錯的是緋村 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.29,0:17:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又沒命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.50,0:17:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在意什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的劍速有些微的遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.90,0:17:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不僅認為\N你心中一定牽掛著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.14,0:17:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說 你洞穿了我的心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.11,0:17:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是不瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.02,0:17:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何你不殺他\N要拘泥於那種無意義的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果這世界柔弱的人\N是死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有強者才存活下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.66,0:18:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也聽不下去了\N滿口胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 你的功夫確實是超一流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.77,0:18:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在人生這個道場上\N你只是個包尿片的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱者就該死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看看劍心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是為了使弱者\N能幸福生活而戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是賭命而戰的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.05,0:18:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓弱者能幸福生活而戰\N你說的話太玄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.92,0:18:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以理解 我真的無法理解緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.23,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護弱者 不殺人 逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的一切都難以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你特別的執著這點哦  宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.57,0:18:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是因為「不殺人」這句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觸動了你內心的什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.98,0:18:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人不眨眼的人對那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.41,0:18:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不會抱持任何關心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心底深處…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是憤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎應該不存在憤怒情緒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是不是講太多了？緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟平時的小弟弟不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…是哪裏不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.21,0:19:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出招了 我是不忌諱殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次你是絕對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.93,0:19:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是怎麼了 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.00,0:19:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 緋村 您等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.27,0:19:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草鞋斷了  您自己休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得替換的草鞋在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼不攻擊呢 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.05,0:19:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才就算你攻擊他\N也算不上卑鄙哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼講話象起齊藤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.99,0:20:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像他那樣全身是破綻\N反而讓人難以出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.76,0:20:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是 我想趁現在療傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.97,0:20:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰 你綁得太用力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題 這不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.45,0:20:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也真落魄\N竟然讓敵人為我療傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.42,0:20:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意 不論是誰\N受傷都應該治療的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.59,0:20:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後我還是贏不了宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.13,0:20:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠無法成為\N志志雄大人的貼身侍者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.80,0:20:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嚴重的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.24,0:20:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換成別人 早昏過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你認為如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.51,0:20:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.45,0:21:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的除了快樂以外\N什麼感情都缺少的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最初我也搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人心裏在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.09,0:21:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是剛才他看來有點像是\N感情受到動搖的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.29,0:21:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許他並非缺乏感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.03,0:21:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是因為某種原因\N把感情封印在心底的深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,封印？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.87,0:21:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他自己也沒察覺到\N無意識之中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.37,0:21:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思？
